        "TileImage": "$($repository 2af0e3d2-86d6-421a-95d8-5dacb67cae60).Image",
        "Description": "Church of Sapienza is wrongfull. Many say that the priest and other workers are in deal with local mafia. Our client is a local activist, who is very.. very unpleasant with current church. He hired us to get rid of them. With a small addition - disguised as the priest. Pretty ironic, isn&apos;t it? \rBut don&apos;t go too far, because you will probably like it.",
